COMMERCE TRUST COMPANY v. Cora JORDAN et al. No. 939. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Feb. 8, 1934. Gotwals, Gibson, Killey & Gibson, of Muskogee, Okl. (Hugh M. Hiller, of Kansas City, Mo., on the brief), for appellant. Clark Nichols, of Eufaula, Okl., for ap-pellees.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on stipulation.
